&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain a healthy pipeline of services opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accurately forecast bookings and associated revenue against established targets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive services attachment on new software opportunities and expansion within existing accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Partnering on strategic customer opportunities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
