&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join Collibra Public Sector&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Collibra Public Sector is looking for an experienced Sales Operations Manager to join our team.&amp;nbsp; This role interacts with all aspects of our public sector subsidiary - sales, service, finance, accounting, human resources, and information technology.&amp;nbsp; The Operations Manager ensures that the public sector systems and processes align with, and help deliver on, our mission to serve US federal customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Public Sector Operations Manager will prepare accurate forecasts and reports.&amp;nbsp; More importantly, the Operations Manager will recommend process improvements that help Collibra Public Sector as we scale up the business.&amp;nbsp; The Operations Manager will incorporate automation and AI to improve decision-making, increase seller productivity, and remove friction from the sales process.&amp;nbsp; The Operations Manager will be the recognized expert and advisor for sellers to prepare accurate quotes using Salesforce CPQ.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Operations Manager will interact with our Finance team to ensure all vendor transactions are properly approved, accounted for, and budgeted.&amp;nbsp; The Operations Manager will prepare periodic reports for the Public Sector General Manager as well as our parent company finance groups.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role requires strong commercial judgment, analytical depth, operational rigor, and the ability to translate complexity into scalable solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This can be a fully remote role, but someone in the greater Washington, DC area is preferred.&lt;/p&gt;
