&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Joining Collibra’s Product Security team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Collibra is seeking a Senior Product Security Engineer to join our high-impact team. You will be a key individual responsible for identifying vulnerabilities and providing expert remediation consulting for our global product development teams. This role provides critical technical leadership and oversight, ensuring Collibra continues to deliver secure, resilient products and services to our customers. You will act as an application security evangelist, partnering with engineers to accelerate secure time-to-value while leveraging cutting-edge AI and MCP to create context-aware security automation.&lt;/p&gt;
