&lt;li&gt;Application security for products and/or features supported by your assigned development teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performing security testing and triaging findings identified by SAST, SCA, IAST, DAST, and penetration tests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage AI and MCP to create intelligent, context-aware security guidance and automation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Providing remediation consulting services to assigned development teams.&lt;/li&gt;
